{"page_content": "\u25cf  If  the  Content  Head  does  not  complete  the  review  within  12  hours  of  \nreceiving\n \nthe\n \ndraft,\n \nthe\n \nreview\n \nstage\n \nwill\n \nbe\n \nskipped\n \nand\n \nthe\n \narticle\n \nwill\n \nproceed\n \nto\n \nthe\n \nnext\n \nstage.\n  \u25cf  Failure  to  respond  within  12  hours  will  be  recorded  and  evaluated  in  the  \nmonthly\n \nperformance\n \nreview.\n  \u25cf  If  the  Content  Head  cannot  complete  the  review  within  24  hours  for  reasons  \nincluding\n \nbut\n \nnot\n \nlimited\n \nto\n \nillness,\n \ninjury,\n \nor\n \npersonal\n \ncircumstances,\n \nthis\n \nmust\n \nbe\n \ncommunicated\n \nin\n \nadvance\n \nand\n \nwill\n \nalso\n \nbe\n \nrecorded\n \nfor\n \nthe\n \nperformance\n \nreview.\n  \u25cf  The  12-hour  and  24-hour  windows  begin  from  the  moment  the  draft  status  \nis\n \nreported\n \nto\n \nthe\n \nContent\n \nHead.\n  \n2.4  CEO  Involvement  \u25cf  The  CEO  may  review  an  article  in  place  of  the  Content  Head  depending  on  \navailability.\n \nThis\n \nis\n \nnot\n \na\n \nrequired\n \nstep\n \nand\n \ndoes\n \nnot\n \ngate\n \nthe\n \neditorial\n \nprocess.\n  \u25cf  The  Content  Head  is  the  primary  decision-maker  for  advancing  articles  \nthrough\n \nthis\n \nstage.\n \nThe\n \nCEO's\n \nreview,\n \nwhen\n \nit\n \noccurs,\n \nis\n \nsupplementary\n \nbut\n \ncan\n \noverride\n \nthe\n \nContent\n \nHead\u2019s\n \ndecision.\n \n \nDocument  Prepared  by:  Zay  Bhone  Hlyan  \nApproved\n \nby:\n \n-\n \nEffective\n \nDate:\n \nMay\n \n2026\n \nNext\n \nReview\n \nDate:\n \nMay\n \n2027\n \n \nSincerely,  \n \nFact\n \nHub\n \nMyanmar\n \n \nThis\n \nletter\n \nserves\n \nas\n \nan\n \nofficial\n \nstatement\n \nfrom\n \nFact", "metadata": {"producer": "Skia/PDF m149 Google Docs Renderer", "creator": "PyPDF", "creationdate": "", "title": "Editorial Override", "source": "FactHubMyanmar_EditorialWorkflowUpdate.pdf", "total_pages": 4, "page": 3, "page_label": "4", "author_or_company": "FACT HUB MYANMAR", "document_type": "Policy Update", "date_or_year": "Unknown", "page_number": 3, "start_index": 0}}